{"tid":1617027,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張達明：引緊急法推禁蒙面法把香港推向萬劫不復","createTime":"2019-10-03T15:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T16:27:08.000Z","uid":125193,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a2e2b779d2046d70918ca55d3bbbfd2db108f7e","tid":1617027,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:20:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484122-20191003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484122-20191003.htm&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0Gb%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=ce6c861c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484122-20191003.htm&h=0992d53e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484122-20191003.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n有消息指，政府將引用緊急法推行禁蒙面法。香港大學法律學院首席講師張達明表示，引用緊急法推行禁蒙面法只會將香港推入萬劫不復的地步，政府是下一個非常大的賭注，因為現時的問題並非法律問題，而是政治問題，立禁蒙面法不但未必止暴制亂，更是向全世界宣示，香港政府不會再遵從法律程序處理法律問題，是一個很壞的先例。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，曾和金融界人士溝通過，不論禁蒙面法立法內容多麽局限也好，設立禁蒙面法，許多投資者都會考慮撤資，因為已經向全世界展示了，香港的法律是可以隨時更改，投資者亦十分擔心政府有機會實行外匯管制，會令他們十分擔心。"},{"pid":"3afd4383a216d17439629326c85c5aa647819384","tid":1617027,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c812cb0bb6bacfea33beb973d8ce4e344ca3e1d","tid":1617027,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a2e2b779d2046d70918ca55d3bbbfd2db108f7e","tid":1617027,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:20:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484122-20191003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fne